tags: [ virsh, qemu, kvm, virt-manager, libvert ]
---

```sh
virsh list --all  # list domains associated with ~/.local/share/images/

sudo virsh list --all  # list domains associated with /var/lib/libvirt/images/

virsh undefine domain_name --remove-all-storage  # remove a domain completely

virsh start domain_name

virsh shutdown domain_name
```

